	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			As I'm sure you are all aware, after the latest patch the Shadowed Men appeared. These are not your average monster, in fact something is very wrong here. These things drop unequippable weapons (altough I've heard that Necro pets can equip some of them) and all manner of strange things happen concerning them. It is my belief that these invisible devils are attempting to take over Norrath. Look around, you'll find them everywhere. They are in fact quite strong. Many of them possess casting abilities, direct damage and healing, leading me to believe that there are different caster classes and cleric/monk/druid types. could these things be related to humans in some way? They seem to have a range of possible abilities that is larger than any other race except humans. I believe that the books carried by some of them are keys to solving this mystery. If anyone kills a shadowed man and manages to obtain one of these books, please post the contents. 
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
